Field Detail

sourceEntityKey

protected java.lang.String sourceEntityKey
The source entity key through which constarint is related. e.g. Used in case of foreign key constraint in one to many relation.

targetEntityKey

protected java.lang.String targetEntityKey
The target entity key through which constraint is related. Used in case of many to many relation.Both source and target entity key is entered in the intermediate table.
